extendedInfo.description: If you are Maroon 5's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Maroon 5's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Maroon 5's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Maroon 5's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :) -------------------------------- Main Features -------------------------------- - Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics -------------------------------- List of albums -------------------------------- - Songs About Jane - It Won't Be Soon Before Long - Hands All Over - Overexposed -------------------------------- List of lyrics -------------------------------- - Back At Your Door - Beautiful Goodbye - Better That We Break - Can't Stop - Come Away To The Water - Daylight - Doin' Dirt - Don't Know Nothing - Figure It Out - Fortune Teller - Get Back In My Life - Give A Little More - Goodnight Goodnight - Hands All Over - Harder To Breathe - How - I Can't Lie - If I Ain't Got You (Live) - If I Never See Your Face Again - If You Only Knew - Infatuation - Is Anybody Out There - Just A Feeling - Kiss - Kiwi - Ladykiller - Last Chance - Let's Stay Together - Little Of Your Time - Losing My Mind - Love Somebody - Lucky Strike - Makes Me Wonder - Misery - Miss You, Love You - Moves Like Jagger - Must Get Out - Never Gonna Leave This Bed - No Curtain Call - Not Coming Home - Not Falling Apart - Nothing Lasts Forever - One More Night - Out Of Goodbyes - Payphone - Ragdoll - Runaway - Sad - Secret - She Will Be Loved - Shiver - Story - Stutter - Sunday Morning - Sweetest Goodbye - Tangled - The Air That I Breathe - The Man Who Never Lied - The Sun - The Way I Was - This Love - Through With You - Tickets - Until You're Over Me - Wake Up Call - Wasted Years - Wipe Your Eyes - Woman - Won't Go Home Without You
